Description: converts Amiga executables to ADF disk images
 exe2adf converts Amiga executable (.exe) files into bootable ADF
 (Amiga Disk File) disk images, suitable for use with Amiga emulators
 or real hardware.
 .
 Created by Bonefish of the demo group Reality in 2015, exe2adf
 supports optional features such as boot-time text display, custom disk
 labels, directory inclusion, custom bootblocks, palette configuration,
 and sector allocation map display.
